WEBVTT

00:07:58.625 --> 00:08:01.611
If you work for the government,
I want you to pass regulation."

00:08:01.635 --> 00:08:02.895
Everybody had a job.

00:08:02.919 --> 00:08:05.042
"Each of you, all of you,
have a role to play

00:08:05.066 --> 00:08:07.518
in protecting these places
for future generations."

00:08:08.161 --> 00:08:10.248
Each of you, all of you.

00:08:11.154 --> 00:08:12.304
I love that.

00:08:14.339 --> 00:08:16.601
That's the plan --
simple, three-point plan.

00:08:17.585 --> 00:08:19.387
I think we can do the same.

00:08:19.411 --> 00:08:21.494
So, this was the headline
when Obama created

00:08:21.518 --> 00:08:25.276
the Papahanaumokuakea National Monument:

00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:28.165
"Lots to see, but good luck
trying to get there."

00:08:28.593 --> 00:08:33.307
But like Mather, we should focus
on the technology of our time,